

The routes start with /api i.e. http://IP/api/product 

YOU CAN USE npm start to start the server.
YOU MIGHT HAVE TO update the creds for mongodb server.

/api/product/ => POST => name and status to add a new product.
		 GET  => get all products.

/api/product/enabled => GET => get all products that have status enabled.
/api/product/disabled=> GET => get "                           " disabled.

/api/product/id/status => PUT => set the product with id to a value status.

/api/product/id => DELETE => delete the object.
		   GET    => gets the object with id.
